rows.label: qst701602_msg0002
rows.name:
I'll just have to show everyone what
I can really do, won't I?

rows.label: qst701602_msg0003
rows.name:
Yes, I can feel some of my passion
coming back to me now...

rows.label: qst701602_msg0004
rows.name:
You're all heading back to the inn
to brainstorm some ideas, yes?

rows.label: qst701602_msg0005
rows.name:
Then I will do the same. I think I've
already got a few surefire winners
up my sleeve!

rows.label: qst701602_msg0102
rows.name: I think I'm good to go as well.

rows.label: qst701602_msg0103
rows.name:
Shall we begin Adel Olgo's
Great Iiran Cook-Off?

rows.label: qst701602_msg0202
rows.name:
It doesn't seem like you have all of
your ingredients yet.

rows.label: qst701602_msg0203
rows.name:
I think I'm all ready on my side, but
I'm more than happy to wait until
you're done.
